select u.first_name,id.item_name,oi.quantity,od.ordered_on
from order_details od
join ordered_items oi
on od.order_id = oi.order_id
join item_details id
on id.item_id = oi.item_id
join user_details u
on u.user_id = od.user_id
where u.user_id = 5;
